trans-unit.source: Represents controls that act as containers for a collection of child elements.
trans-unit.target: Representerer kontroller som brukes som beholdere for en samling av underordnede elementer.

trans-unit.source: The children of this control support <xref href="System.Windows.Automation.GridItemPattern"></xref> and are organized in a two-dimensional logical coordinate system that can be traversed by row and column.
trans-unit.target: Underordnede til dette kontrollere støtte <xref href="System.Windows.Automation.GridItemPattern"> </xref> og ordnes i et todimensjonal logiske koordinatsystem kan traversert av rad- og.

trans-unit.source: GridPattern does not support active manipulation of a grid; the <xref:System.Windows.Automation.TransformPattern>control pattern is required for this functionality.
trans-unit.target: GridPattern støtter ikke aktiv manipulering av et rutenett. den <xref:System.Windows.Automation.TransformPattern>kontrollen mønsteret kreves for denne funksjonaliteten.</xref:System.Windows.Automation.TransformPattern>

trans-unit.source: See [Control Pattern Mapping for UI Automation Clients](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md) for examples of controls that may support this control pattern.
trans-unit.target: Se [kontrollen mønsteret tilordning for Brukergrensesnittet automatiseringsklienter](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md) for eksempler på kontroller som støtter denne kontrollen mønsteret.

trans-unit.source: This pattern must be from an <xref:System.Windows.Automation.AutomationElement> with an <xref:System.Windows.Automation.AutomationElementMode> reference in order to get current values.

trans-unit.source: If the <xref:System.Windows.Automation.AutomationElement> was obtained using <xref:System.Windows.Automation.AutomationElementMode>, it contains only cached data, and attempting to get the current value of any property raises an exception.
trans-unit.target: Hvis den <xref:System.Windows.Automation.AutomationElement>ble hentet ved hjelp av <xref:System.Windows.Automation.AutomationElementMode>, den inneholder bare bufrede data, og forsøk på å hente gjeldende verdi for en egenskap viser et unntak.</xref:System.Windows.Automation.AutomationElementMode> </xref:System.Windows.Automation.AutomationElement>

trans-unit.source: Retrieves an <xref href="System.Windows.Automation.AutomationElement"></xref> that represents the specified cell.
trans-unit.target: Henter en <xref href="System.Windows.Automation.AutomationElement"> </xref> som representerer den angitte cellen.

trans-unit.source: Grid coordinates are zero-based with the upper left (or upper right cell depending on locale) having coordinates (0,0).
trans-unit.target: Rutenett koordinatene er nullbasert med øvre venstre (eller cellen øverst til høyre avhengig nasjonal innstilling) med koordinater (0,0).

trans-unit.source: If a cell is empty, a [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uiautomation](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-uiautomation-md.md)] element is still returned in order to support retrieval of the <xref:System.Windows.Automation.GridItemPattern.GridItemPatternInformation.ContainingGrid%2A> property for that cell.
trans-unit.target: Hvis en celle er tom, en [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uiautomation](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-uiautomation-md.md)] elementet returneres fremdeles for å støtte henting av den <xref:System.Windows.Automation.GridItemPattern.GridItemPatternInformation.ContainingGrid%2A>egenskapen for denne cellen.</xref:System.Windows.Automation.GridItemPattern.GridItemPatternInformation.ContainingGrid%2A>

trans-unit.source: This is possible when the layout of child elements in the grid is similar to a ragged array as shown here.
trans-unit.target: Dette er mulige når oppsettet for underordnede elementer i rutenettet ligner en uregelmessige matrise som vises her.

trans-unit.source: ![Windows Explorer view showing ragged layout.](~/add/media/uia-gridpattern-ragged-array.PNG "Windows Explorer view showing ragged layout.")
trans-unit.target: ![Windows Utforsker Vis viser uregelmessige oppsett. ] (~/add/media/uia-gridpattern-ragged-array.PNG "Windows Utforsker visningen viser uregelmessige oppsett.")
